    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=ContDiffAt.eventually#doc\">docs#ContDiffAt.eventually</a> does seem to be exactly what I was missing, thanks!</p>",
